0010 REM "BMM - Operation Code Maintenance
0020 REM "Program BMM.AA"
0022 REM "+-----------------------------------------------------------+"
0024 REM "| ADD+ON Software, Inc. Advantage/V Version 6.0.0 - 15May96 |"
